snippet.title: AlanBeckerTutorials
snippet.description:
My name is Alan Becker, most famous for "Animator vs. Animation", a viral video from 2006. Here is where I put my tutorials. I teach animation using Adobe Flash/Animate, and some Photoshop and Minecraft stuff.

If you would like to contact me, visit
http://www.alanbecker.net/contact-me

If you are wondering what equipment I use for my videos, click here:
http://www.alanbecker.net/my-gear
